Usage:

    script/generate reservation_calendar [RESERVATION_MODEL DATE_MODEL VIEW_NAME] [--use_jquery] [--static_only]

  This will create:
      
    # static files
      public/stylesheets/reservation_calendar.css
      public/javascripts/reservation_calendar.js
      
    # Unless --static-only option is given
    # MVC and supporting files (depending on model and view name)
      app/models/reservation.rb
      app/models/dates.rb
      app/controllers/calendar_controller.rb
      app/views/calendar
      app/views/calendar/index.html.erb
      app/helpers/calendar_helper.rb
      db/migrate
      db/migrate/XXXX_create_reservations_and_dates.rb
      route map.calendar